				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="whome is not online. Last active: 6/1/2004 5:03:36 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=whome">whome</a><br></td>
